    {
      "_id": "dcd92fde274e82ee",
      "name": "Martial Attack",
      "sort": 3,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-8070-8105-e5c292df882c\">A creature makes a Martial Attack when they make an Attack Check using a Weapon or Unarmed Strike against a target’s Defense.</p><ul id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80f5-9907-e4cb818ac3ac\" class=\"bulleted-list\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><strong>Unarmed Strike:</strong> A Martial Attack made using any part of a creature’s own body, such as a Punch, Elbow, Kick, Knee, or Headbutt.</li></ul><ul id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80a9-a63f-db30d11abfde\" class=\"bulleted-list\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><strong>Weapon Attack:</strong> A Martial Attack made using a Weapon, such as an Axe, Sword, or Bow. You can draw a Weapon as part of an Attack made using it.</li></ul>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 3,
        "show": true
      },
      "type": "text",
      "system": {},
      "image": {},
      "video": {
